author: Nexcell Pride
text:
Wow, an intense stream ever :_ちょうちょ:
BGM Opening: Summer Triangle.

This time, Rushia-daitenshi didn't get at least the 3rd place than previous streams of this game, but despite the result she at least seems too calm and with a good sense of humor.

Who said about the Necromancers can't laugh, smile or grin? If that was true, so Rushia broke her character's shell.
This makes it ever closer to those who see her. :_きゅん:

And "Supaachaato Orei Time" was too long and more interesting, because Rushia told us about Yesterday's Cross-collab between Hololive and 2434. It was pure Daiya 💎

And... Personally talking... Well, nobody asked me about one Superchat with the following message: "Stop the jokes. Not pettan, not Boing boing, she's just an Angel enclosed inside a Necromancer body"
Please forgive me about the previous point, but you can ask me already... 😳❤️

author: Amai Ta. Yume
text: Thank you for the lovely stream! Thank you for all the Translators, EN and JP bros who kept supporting Rushia! Let's all do our best in the future! For Rushia, Thank you for everything you have done for us yet again! I'm proud to be a fandead member and hope to spend more time with you! We'll always keep on cheering for you and hope that everything will lead to a better life than usual! Take care, Rushia! See you next time!
